Hosting the Software behind paywalls or subscription services

Using the Software to generate revenue (e.g., ad‑supported sites, cryptocurrency mining)

Incorporating the Software into a commercial product or service

If you wish to use MiniGames commercially, please contact us to discuss licensing options.

4. Attribution
Any fork or public instance of the Software must retain this license and clearly credit the original authors. A visible link to the official repository must be provided in a conspicuous location (e.g., the footer, about page, or README).

Required attribution format:

text
